    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Need a tool belt that can help with the most difficult home improvement jobs? This deluxe-sized suede tool belt has multiple compartments for small and large tools. No handy work is too hard with this deluxe tool belt! The suede tool belt has many compartments for nails, drills, hammers, or screwdrivers. Larger power tools are able to fit in the main compartments so a variety of tools can be easily carried. Specifically, there are 4 large pockets for nails and 6 pockets for small tools as well as 2 nickel finish metal hammer holders. The belt is adjustable through waist sizes of 30&quot;-46&quot; and secures tightly. The leather tape pocket holds up to a 30&quot; tape measure and there are reinforced corners for durability</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">9 Pocket Carpenter Tool Belt Heavy Duty Suede Leather Fits Hammer And Nails</h2>\n  <p>Need a tool belt that can help with the most difficult home improvement jobs? This deluxe-sized suede tool belt has multiple compartments for small and large tools. No handy work is too hard with this deluxe tool belt!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>Deluxe Custom Suede Variety Tool Storage Belt and Bags</li>\n    <li>Multiple compartments for tools such as hammers, nails, drills, and screwdrivers with double main compartments</li>\n    <li>Perfectly sized for easy transportation of hefty tools</li>\n    <li>Ideal companion for Deluxe Suede Tool Bag by Universal Tool</li>\n    <li>Convenient storage for carpenters, handy workers, and DIY jobs</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/Tools/AS2103A_deluxe_tool_pouch_12pkt_detail_01.jpg\" alt=\"Need a tool belt that can help with the most difficult home improvement jobs\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> 67105</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 614944575564</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> Adjustable</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>The suede tool belt has many compartments for nails, drills, hammers, or screwdrivers. Larger power tools are able to fit in the main compartments so a variety of tools can be easily carried. Specifically, there are 4 large pockets for nails and 6 pockets for small tools as well as 2 nickel finish metal hammer holders. The belt is adjustable through waist sizes of 30&quot;-46&quot; and secures tightly. The leather tape pocket holds up to a 30&quot; tape measure and there are reinforced corners for durability. Measuring at 22 inches long, this tool belt is an ideal size to transport several tools to any type of construction site.</p>\n  <p>Order this Deluxe Suede Tool Belt to fix all your home improvement jobs. You will have the confidence to do it yourself when all your tools are by your side and conveniently stored!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "Need a tool belt that can help with the most difficult home improvement jobs? This deluxe-sized suede tool belt has multiple compartments for small and large tools. No handy work is too hard with this deluxe tool belt! The suede tool belt has many compartments for nails, drills, hammers, or screwdrivers. Larger power tools are able to fit in the main compartments so a variety of tools can be easily carried. Specifically, there are 4 large pockets for nails and 6 pockets for small tools as well as 2 nickel finish metal hammer holders. The belt is adjustable through waist sizes of 30\"-46\" and secures tightly. The leather tape pocket holds up to a 30\" tape measure and there are reinforced corners for durability.",
